Elemental Body	KEY:Elemental Body ~ Element-Infused	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Defensive										DESC:Element-infused creatures' bodies gain some of the qualities of elementals. Each time an element-infused creature is exposed to a poison, paralysis, sleep, or stunning effect, it has a 25%% chance to avoid it. In addition, there is a 25%% chance that a sneak attack or critical hit deals no extra damage.																															SOURCEPAGE:p.112
