Breath Weapon	KEY:Breath Weapon ~ Fire-Infused		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural			DEFINE:BreathWeaponDC|0	DEFINE:BreathWeaponDice|0	DESC:A fire-infused creature can breathe a 30-foot-long cone of fire once every 1d4 rounds. Every creature in the area must succeed on a Reflex saving throw (DC %1) or take %2d6 points of fire damage. A successful Reflex save halves this fire damage.|BreathWeaponDC|BreathWeaponDice									BONUS:VAR|BreathWeaponDC|10+(HD/2)+CON	BONUS:VAR|BreathWeaponDice|max(HD/2,1)	BONUS:VAR|BreathWeaponDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Breath Weapon)	SOURCEPAGE:p.111	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(30' cone of fire, %1d6, DC %2)|BreathWeaponDice|BreathWeaponDC
Heat			KEY:Heat ~ Fire-Infused				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.AttackOption										DESC:A fire-infused creature generates so much heat that its mere touch deals an additional 1d6 points of fire damage. A fire-infused creature's metallic weapons also conduct this heat.																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.111	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(1d6)
Firewalk		KEY:Firewalk ~ Fire-Infused			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural												DESC:A fire-infused creature can climb an object on fire as though it had a climb speed equal to its highest speed. Furthermore, it can fly at its highest speed with perfect maneuverability so long as it remains in contact with fire, and it can walk on flames at its highest speed, as though walking on air via the Air Walk spell.																											SOURCEPAGE:p.112
Fire Healing	KEY:Fire Healing ~ Fire-Infused		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.ModifyHP										DESC:A fire-infused creature regains 1 hit point for each full round that it remains in contact with fire. When struck by a magical fire effect, the fire-infused creature heals 1 point of damage per 10 points of damage that the fire effect would otherwise deal.																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.112

